GROZNIY CITY - Bomb/Defuse

Counter-Terrorists: Prevent Terrorists
from bombing the old bus with weapon
crates.

Terrorists: The Terrorist carrying the
C4 must destroy one of the bus with
weapon crates. 

Other Notes: There are 2 bomb sites
in the mission.

Other Notes: MADE IN RUSSIA!
